p: We analyzed the anonymized flight itineraries of all travelers from SEA into China between 2005 and 2015, using data obtained from the International Air Transport Association (IATA). As most travel is temporary, and local residents of SEA and Chinese travelers returning from SEA might have different risks of dengue infection and importation [ 23], we obtained annual statistics of the nationality of travelers entering China from the China National Tourism Administration to estimate the monthly volume of air travelers by nationality to further delineate the risk. The database is described in the Materials and Methods section in S1 Appendix.
